@zdevito After inspecting the compilation log, there seems to be a few issues with the generated aten_schema.cpp file:

torch/csrc/jit/generated/aten_schema.cpp: https://gist.githubusercontent.com/yf225/2500ee8d088fa82b8500e298e1c54c0e/raw/5856db317f6128f5c1d1f79e514b96ea55a2a753/generated_aten_schema.cpp

I suspect that fixing the "character constant too long for its type" error for all the odict_keys will also fix the other errors.
